{"tid":1329752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《721和理非除咗遊行有咩做？！》全部和理非唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T11:48:36.000Z","uid":269743,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"480dfa935385c0120660975bd1ce2dc57bbf3ce9","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"幫手帶物資！幫手帶物資！幫手帶物資！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申和理非中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一班年青人犧牲自己嘅前途<br />\n為香港人企到咁前<br />\n我只能夠做和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每一次內心都會有種過唔到自己嘅感覺&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n記得中信大廈嘅時候， TG group不停話要哮喘藥<br />\n附近好難買，我就即刻落樓下買咗十支帶過去<br />\n可惜已經太遲喇￼去到已經知道物資部要撤<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我就發現<br />\n物資其實唔係真正需要嘅時候先至去買<br />\n到時係買唔切㗎喇<br />\n<strong>最好嘅方法就係由和理非早上遊行嘅時候帶過去</strong>&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n每次遊完行就放低少少物資，已經成為我習慣<br />\n當係贖罪券又好乜都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家有錢出錢 有力出力</span><br />\n<br />\n講真，每次幾百蚊，食餐飯都冇咗啦～<br />\n但係前線就會多一分保護！<br />\n<br />\n我之前會帶哮喘藥，生理鹽水，急救用品<br />\n最近我會帶六角匙（雖然唔知點解係六角匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但次次都有人高呼）較剪，保鮮紙<br />\n<br />\n然後將自己當日帶嘅長遮放低<br />\n<br />\n<strong>希望大家都可以喺遊行以外盡少少綿力</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果有發夢夢到物資部真正需要乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩留言講下，我依然會盡我最大努力做後援<br />\n<br />\n<code>對準五大訴求\n缺一不可\n721金鐘見</code>"},{"pid":"581858167dafc7de2febc8ce44cc5a10f8ecf99e","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n721見"},{"pid":"b729920be88d053343eb67d667660feffa62a4b4","tid":1329752,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"721推土機出動<br />\n================<br />\n堅守五大訴求 勿分化勿指責 <br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n建議大家自備物資 做流動物資站<br />\n頭盔 眼罩 口罩 毛巾 是啤衫<br />\n我無嘢講 我要見律師<br />\n【721整合】721整合Post！全部推哂上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329038\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329038</a>"},{"pid":"c741ad3a34a846fd33f5ee9489e14ba6a789cf6d","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:08:35.000Z","msg":"重點係和理非個樣冇咁容易俾龜逗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c0e0fa707434e21ae6fe912068764846b72749","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"俾返721嘅post上熱門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a43e3219483db0b5f12583761681e77a603017f","tid":1329752,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"477c89c1793271fd02f19b8d18245d0719d56925","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"索帶索帶索帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0ef6b23f1b977bfbb8f8f4b66074e5f8a7ca5b","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:17:31.000Z","msg":"推721721啊！"},{"pid":"253e334b9d293e0e18ae49a83bc6e2fc9456bb0b","tid":1329752,"uid":269743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZ6sWnv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr